      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — FDA generic centrifugal pump",
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry measurements acquired at 3 L/min and 2500 RPM compared against CFD predictions. Normalized RMS velocity error of 4.2% across 12 measurement planes. Validation activity conducted on 2024-Q3 model build; solver version 2026-Q1 update applied post-validation without re-execution of this comparison."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-rh-index-bench-2024",
      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Relative hemolysis index bench validation — 5 operating points",
      "description": "Bench-measured plasma-free haemoglobin used to compute RH index at 5 flow-speed combinations. CFD-predicted RH within 12% of measured values across all operating points. Acceptance criterion RH < 1 satisfied. Power-law hemolysis coefficients from Giersiepen 1990 used in model; revised coefficients from 2023 ISO 10993-17 addendum not incorporated."
    },
    {
      "id": "https://uofa.net/synth/validation/morrison-mesh-convergence-2024",
