      "name": "Mesh convergence study — Richardson extrapolation on shear stress QoI",
      "description": "Three-level mesh refinement study (4.2M, 11.7M, 28.4M cells) with Richardson extrapolation yielding GCI of 2.1% for volume-averaged shear stress. Discretization error assessed as within MRL 2 requirements."
    }
  ],
