      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver is a commercially validated CFD code with documented version control and regression test suite. MRL 2 requires Gradation 1: documented solver identity and version.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2026 R1 used throughout. Version identity recorded in simulation log files. Vendor-supplied regression test certificates on file. Requirement document references ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 2 SQA criteria; no update to criteria mandated by subsequent errata is noted, but the SQA activities performed satisfy the 2018 baseline requirements as cited."
    },
    {
