      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "MRL 2 requires Gradation 1: manufacturer benchmark test results available demonstrating solver correctness on canonical flows.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2026 R1 benchmark suite includes lid-driven cavity, backward-facing step, and rotating disk flow cases. Results consistent with published reference solutions to within 1%. Numerical code verification requirement satisfied per ASME V&V 40-2018 Section 5.3.1 as cited in the governing requirement document."
