      "rationale": "All simulations run to residual convergence of 1×10⁻⁵ for continuity and momentum equations. Mass imbalance below 0.01% in all cases. Convergence history recorded in simulation log files and archived. Requirement document references ASME V&V 40-2018 Section 5.4 solver error criteria."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
