      "acceptanceCriteria": "MRL 2 requires Gradation 1: model form assumptions documented.",
      "rationale": "Not assessed at this stage. Acceptable at MRL 2. SST k-ω turbulence model and Giersiepen 1990 power-law hemolysis model selected based on prior literature for centrifugal pump hemolysis CFD. Model form assumptions are documented in the simulation plan but formal model form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018."
    },
    {
