      "rationale": "Not assessed at this stage. Acceptable at MRL 2. Fluid properties, boundary conditions, and geometric parameters are sourced from the FDA generic pump benchmark dataset and documented in the simulation plan. Formal sensitivity analysis of model inputs is not required at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 2."
